						               													<description>The Klingon Ship Recognition Manual expands on the ships types seen in the base game Star Trek: Starship Tactical Combat Simulator, adding new variants for almost every Klingon ship in that product, as well as adding a number of new fighters, ships, and bases.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;As with the base Star Trek: Starship Tactical Combat Simulator itself, this is ostensibly an &amp;quot;expansion&amp;quot; for the Role Playing game, in that it provides more data than just the combat element requires.  3-dimension views are provided for all craft, along with extensive historical notes and background.  The cover of this 48-page product features a cutaway of the Klingon D-20 'Deathrite' cruiser.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Indicating the clear tie to the wargame, the last page presents a sheet of counters that you can photocopy and mount on cardboard for use with the tactical game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Expands&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    Star Trek: Starship Tactical Combat Simulator&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
